001package com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.response.historyLog;
002
003import com.google.common.base.Preconditions;
004import com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.annotations.HistoryLogProps;
005import com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.helpers.Bytes;
006
007@HistoryLogProps(
008    opCode = 21,
009    displayName = "Extended Bolus Portion Complete",
010    usedByAndroid = true
011)
012public class BolexCompletedHistoryLog extends HistoryLog {
013    
014    private int completionStatus;
015    private int bolusId;
016    private float iob;
017    private float insulinDelivered;
018    private float insulinRequested;
019    
020    public BolexCompletedHistoryLog() {}
021    
022    public BolexCompletedHistoryLog(long pumpTimeSec, long sequenceNum, int completionStatus, int bolusId, float iob, float insulinDelivered, float insulinRequested) {
023        this.cargo = buildCargo(pumpTimeSec, sequenceNum, completionStatus, bolusId, iob, insulinDelivered, insulinRequested);
024        this.pumpTimeSec = pumpTimeSec;
025        this.sequenceNum = sequenceNum;
026        this.completionStatus = completionStatus;
027        this.bolusId = bolusId;
028        this.iob = iob;
029        this.insulinDelivered = insulinDelivered;
030        this.insulinRequested = insulinRequested;
031        
032    }
033
034    public int typeId() {
035        return 21;
036    }
037
038    /**
039     * <table border="1">
040     * <caption>Parsed fields for BolexCompletedHistoryLog:</caption>
041     * <tr><td><code>completionStatus</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readShort(raw, 10)</code></td></tr>
042     * <tr><td><code>bolusId</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readShort(raw, 12)</code></td></tr>
043     * <tr><td><code>iob</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readFloat(raw, 14)</code></td></tr>
044     * <tr><td><code>insulinDelivered</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readFloat(raw, 18)</code></td></tr>
045     * <tr><td><code>insulinRequested</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readFloat(raw, 22)</code></td></tr>
046     * </table>
047     */
048    public void parse(byte[] raw) {
049        Preconditions.checkArgument(raw.length == 26);
050        this.cargo = raw;
051        parseBase(raw);
052        this.completionStatus = Bytes.readShort(raw, 10);
053        this.bolusId = Bytes.readShort(raw, 12);
054        this.iob = Bytes.readFloat(raw, 14);
055        this.insulinDelivered = Bytes.readFloat(raw, 18);
056        this.insulinRequested = Bytes.readFloat(raw, 22);
057        
058    }
059
060    
061    /**
062     * <table border="1">
063     * <caption>Byte layout for BolexCompletedHistoryLog.buildCargo(...):</caption>
064     * <tr><th>Offset</th><th>Description</th></tr>
065     * <tr><td>0</td><td><code>new byte[]{21} [element 0]</code></td></tr>
066     * <tr><td>1</td><td><code>new byte[]{0} [element 1]</code></td></tr>
067     * <tr><td>2</td><td><code>toUint32(pumpTimeSec) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
068     * <tr><td>3</td><td><code>toUint32(pumpTimeSec) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
069     * <tr><td>4</td><td><code>toUint32(pumpTimeSec) [byte 2]</code></td></tr>
070     * <tr><td>5</td><td><code>toUint32(pumpTimeSec) [byte 3]</code></td></tr>
071     * <tr><td>6</td><td><code>toUint32(sequenceNum) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
072     * <tr><td>7</td><td><code>toUint32(sequenceNum) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
073     * <tr><td>8</td><td><code>toUint32(sequenceNum) [byte 2]</code></td></tr>
074     * <tr><td>9</td><td><code>toUint32(sequenceNum) [byte 3]</code></td></tr>
075     * <tr><td>10</td><td><code>firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(completionStatus) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
076     * <tr><td>11</td><td><code>firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(completionStatus) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
077     * <tr><td>12</td><td><code>firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(bolusId) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
078     * <tr><td>13</td><td><code>firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(bolusId) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
079     * <tr><td>14</td><td><code>toFloat(iob) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
080     * <tr><td>15</td><td><code>toFloat(iob) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
081     * <tr><td>16</td><td><code>toFloat(iob) [byte 2]</code></td></tr>
082     * <tr><td>17</td><td><code>toFloat(iob) [byte 3]</code></td></tr>
083     * <tr><td>18</td><td><code>toFloat(insulinDelivered) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
084     * <tr><td>19</td><td><code>toFloat(insulinDelivered) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
085     * <tr><td>20</td><td><code>toFloat(insulinDelivered) [byte 2]</code></td></tr>
086     * <tr><td>21</td><td><code>toFloat(insulinDelivered) [byte 3]</code></td></tr>
087     * <tr><td>22</td><td><code>toFloat(insulinRequested) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
088     * <tr><td>23</td><td><code>toFloat(insulinRequested) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
089     * <tr><td>24</td><td><code>toFloat(insulinRequested) [byte 2]</code></td></tr>
090     * <tr><td>25</td><td><code>toFloat(insulinRequested) [byte 3]</code></td></tr>
091     * </table>
092     */
093    public static byte[] buildCargo(long pumpTimeSec, long sequenceNum, int completionStatus, int bolusId, float iob, float insulinDelivered, float insulinRequested) {
094        return Bytes.combine(
095            new byte[]{21, 0},
096            Bytes.toUint32(pumpTimeSec),
097            Bytes.toUint32(sequenceNum),
098            Bytes.firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(completionStatus), 
099            Bytes.firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(bolusId), 
100            Bytes.toFloat(iob), 
101            Bytes.toFloat(insulinDelivered), 
102            Bytes.toFloat(insulinRequested));
103    }
104    
105    public int getCompletionStatus() {
106        return completionStatus;
107    }
108    public int getBolusId() {
109        return bolusId;
110    }
111    public float getIob() {
112        return iob;
113    }
114    public float getInsulinDelivered() {
115        return insulinDelivered;
116    }
117    public float getInsulinRequested() {
118        return insulinRequested;
119    }
120    
121}
